parameters: Clea: Celis-san! I'm glad you're safe!

Psema the Imposter Adventurer: It's a big difference from
when you smelled like pee! I'm genuinely impressed that you
don't let your guard down with your comrades.
Clea: You're Psema...! What did you do to Celis-san!?

Imposter Adventurer Psema: Your beloved Celis-chan is my
obedient slave who will do anything I say.

dog. It's an order. Show me how you can excite me!
Swift Celis: ...I will now serve you in your private area.

embrace her right in front of you, Clea-chan.

Clea: I don't know what you did to Celis-san, but I know
that she will be freed if I defeat you.

Imposter Adventurer Psema: Hahaha, do you really think you
can defeat me? The great senior Celis-chan is no match for
you, huh?

Imposter Adventurer Psema: You should know better than
anyone how strong this person is.

Clea: If it's the manipulated Celis-san, I can win. Besides,
I have my comrades who have adventured with me.

Clea: ...Thanks to everyone. Finally, I was able to corner
Psema.
